{"tid":510277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南京海底撈食客不滿遭怠慢　擲水杯大罵店員「狗眼看人低」","createTime":"2017-12-26T09:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T05:58:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d787a93e2e5d6dec705cb710425894c5eeb2dacb","tid":510277,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T09:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171224/s00004/55c6d89d037cc8b3225d5e0e00fc89a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171224%2Fs00004%2F55c6d89d037cc8b3225d5e0e00fc89a7.jpg&h=90596fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日內地網絡流傳一段短片，片段中一名女子在江蘇南京某海底撈店就餐期間，懷疑因不滿店員沒有給她斟水，憤而擲水杯並破口大罵。<br />\n<br />\n片段所見，這名女子與一名友人就餐期間，突然女子搶過友人水杯擲向地面，並開始夾雜粗言破口大罵店員故意怠慢，批評店員給友人斟了兩杯水，自己卻一杯沒有斟，是「狗眼看人低」。<br />\n<br />\n女子稱自己一個月30天內光顧這家店鋪26天，又指「這兩日已經心情不好，過來吃個飯心情還不好」，最後更要求店員「給我倒10杯水過來，喊10個服務員過來把水喝了，一個人喝一杯」。<br />\n<br />\n該海底撈經理事後接受訪問，指事件對店鋪沒什麽影響，僅是一般的突發事件，當時已經妥當處理，而涉事店員之後也繼續正常上班。<br />\n<br />\n片段流傳後引起內地網民熱議，有網民批評這名女子過分，直指「把人不當人的人一定不是個人」、「花點小錢，都想當大爺」，然而卻有網民表示「打開門做生意就得用心做，不是錢多錢少的問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171224/s00004/1514119980468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171224%2Fs00004%2F1514119980468&d=bGwBNGBWYcdXWdNJwJhMx8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=a92eb913\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171224%2Fs00004%2F1514119980468&h=326ab718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171224/s00004/1514119980468</a>"},{"pid":"6e48d6ab107c1481c77a6c6f958ff26bde062897","tid":510277,"uid":38671,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"如果事件主角係香港人<br />\n個post應該好多正評同好多自稱做服務業既人話香港客點點點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a67f50675b670ecafeb925e622804678c62e3e","tid":510277,"uid":12536,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"30日幫襯26次 係咪食到痴q左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecb1f294c49b1a24057a26419c3acbfcf072771","tid":510277,"uid":52358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"女子稱自己一個月30天內光顧這家店鋪26天<br />\n仲未毒死 果然對元素週期表免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18df40f24fa00d5096075fe18f47d972343fc213","tid":510277,"uid":24140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"返左大陸一排 冇辦法再歧視大陸人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/509790/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/509790/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n入面班支那人唔知點睇呢?"},{"pid":"c081758c7083920feb9ef463b33bfac7fe58800d","tid":510277,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:39:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a9a5892872acb5c6e08a1b14c0cb2578daa4772","tid":510277,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果事件主角係香港人<br />\n個post應該好多正評同好多自稱做服務業既人話香港客點點點<br />\n[img]assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif[/img] [img]assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif[/img] [img]assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif[/img]</blockquote>我地香港人鍾意點就點</blockquote><br />\n扮乜撚啊支狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da57196161b1ada2f15c36ed84fb6b9e4f099344","tid":510277,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18df40f24fa00d5096075fe18f47d972343fc213","tid":510277,"uid":24140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:37:28.000Z","msg":"返左大陸一排 冇辦法再歧視大陸人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg